timefilterControl compact=true column="@timestamp"
| render containerStyle={containerStyle border="  #ec77a8"}

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT
SUM(trafico.totales.traficoOUT)/SUM(trafico.totales.consumoGB) FROM \"prod-mintic-concat\""
| math "SUM_trafico.totales.traficoOUT_/SUM_trafico.totales.consumoGB_"
| metric "Countries" 
  metricFont={font size=48 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center" lHeight=48} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"} metricFormat="0,0.[000]%"
| render
